name: Arb Furbo
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
ARB FURBO is a Decentralised Reflection token designed to reward $FARB Holders with $ARB Tokens. ARB FURBO has a total supply of 1 billion tokens and a circulating supply of 500M tokens - its ecosystem also offers the FURBO Dashboard which allows allows token holders to view their current token balance, rewards received and value of their rewards, all in one place. Offering Other Utilities as well as the AI Contract Auditor, Token Locker, an upcoming NFT Collection etc.

One of the key features of ARB FURBO is the FURBO Dashboard, which is a user-friendly platform that allows token holders to view their current token balance, rewards received, and the value of their rewards. The dashboard provides a comprehensive view of all token-related information in one place, making it easier for users to manage their holdings.
